ax at the start wrapped in a meta tag comment).\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"Create social media content and a full blog post for:\\nBrand: {{ $json.brand_name }}\\nMention Brand: {{ $json.mention_brand }}\\nContent Niche: {{ $json.content_niche }}\\nTopic: {{ $json.selected_topic }}\\nBlog Title: {{ $json.blog_title }}\\nKey Takeaway: {{ $json.key_takeaway }}\\nLead Hook: {{ $json.lead_hook }}\\nAngle: {{ $json.campaign_angle }}\\nTarget Audience: {{ $json.target_audience }}\\nHashtags: {{ JSON.stringify($json.hashtags) }}\\nMood: {{ JSON.stringify($json.mood_keywords) }}\\nWhy Trending: {{ $json.why_trending }}\\n\\nREMEMBER: Follow the branding rules strictly. Every social post must include a comment prompt like 'Comment to get the full blog breakdown on this topic'. Blog content must be ready for WordPress publishing.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
